# AI-Powered Customer Support Ticket System

## Project Overview

This project uses NLP and Machine Learning techniques for customer support ticket analysis, ticket classification, priority prediction, customer segmentation, and Power BI dashboard visualization.

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Scikit-learn
* FastAPI
* Power BI
* NLP
* Hugging Face

